	(text "Resistors are thick film resistors rated for 75V ±1% or better, unless stated otherwise.\nCapacitors are Class II MLCCs rated for 50V ±10% 125°C or better, unless stated otherwise.\nPPTC fuses holds current at 350mA and trips at 750mA, and are rated at 16V.\nUnidirectional TVS diodes clamp at 9.2V (5V) and 19.9V (12V)."
